Title: Confidential
Writer: Michael Brandt (developed by), Derek Haas (developed by), Dick Wolf (created by), Matt Olmstead (created by), Rick Eid, Sharon Lee Watson, Gwen Sigan (story editor), Kinan Copen (story editor)
